OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780074357
OL,3,CSAS chief avoided police referral to
OL,4,Cprotect troop morale, inquiry hears
OL,6,FThe former chief of staff at UK
OL,7,Fspecial forces told a public inquiry
OL,8,Fthat he thought allegations of war
OL,9,Fcrimes involving the SAS were not
OL,10,Fpassed to military police because of
OL,11,Ffears that an investigation might
OL,12,Finterfere with operations and damage
OL,13,Fmorale, new evidence shows.
OL,15,FThe senior officer, who is known to
OL,16,Fthe Afghanistan Inquiry as N2252, was
OL,17,Fchief of staff to the director of the
OL,18,FUK's special forces in 2010 and 2011.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
