PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780074357
OL,3,CSAS chief avoided police referral to
OL,4,Cprotect troop morale, inquiry hears
OL,6,FHe said there was a high degree of
OL,7,Fpressure to deliver because more than
OL,8,F100 British soldiers had been killed
OL,9,Fin Afghanistan in 2010, adding that
OL,10,Fthere was concern about how troops
OL,11,F"had been to lots of funerals".
OL,13,F"We didn't want that to happen again,"
OL,14,Fhe said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
