PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780074357
OL,3,CSAS chief avoided police referral to
OL,4,Cprotect troop morale, inquiry hears
OL,6,FThe testimony came from closed-door
OL,7,Fevidence to the Independent Inquiry
OL,8,Frelating to Afghanistan, which was
OL,9,Flaunched to investigate allegations of
OL,10,Funlawful killings by British Special
OL,11,FForces during deliberate detention
OL,12,Foperations in the early part of the
OL,13,Flate decade.
OL,15,FThe sub-unit UKSF1 specifically came
OL,16,Funder scrutiny in relation to specific
OL,17,Ftactics, techniques and procedures
OL,18,F(TTP) which involved detainees being
OL,19,Fsent back into compounds after being
OL,20,Ftaken into custody.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780074357
OL,3,CSAS chief avoided police referral to
OL,4,Cprotect troop morale, inquiry hears
OL,6,FN2252 expressed concerns that with the
OL,7,FTTP, the balance of care was not
OL,8,Fnecessarily right and instead,
OL,9,Fpriority was placed on the safety of
OL,10,FUK officers over Afghan detainees.
OL,12,F"Having taken them off-target, I think
OL,13,Fwe were maybe legally I don't know,
OL,14,Fbut certainly morally I thought
OL,15,Fresponsible for their wellbeing while
OL,16,Fthey were in the care of UKSF
OL,17,Fdetention," he said.
OL,19,FIn defence of these actions, he said:
OL,20,F"We were not lazy, we were not
OL,21,Freckless, we were not careless."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
