PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780074357
OL,3,CSAS chief avoided police referral to
OL,4,Cprotect troop morale, inquiry hears
OL,6,FAnother witness, who was a senior
OL,7,Foperational advisor at UKSF given the
OL,8,Fcipher N1788, was instructed to
OL,9,Fconduct a review into TTP in 2011.
OL,11,FN1788 suggested there were obvious
OL,12,Fconcerns about the practice and that
OL,13,Fsenior officers in Afghanistan should
OL,14,Fhave been aware.
OL,16,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
