PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780074357
OL,3,CSAS chief avoided police referral to
OL,4,Cprotect troop morale, inquiry hears
OL,6,FFurther evidence was presented
OL,7,Frelating to tensions between sub-units
OL,8,Fof UKSF1 and UKSF3 and the allegations
OL,9,Fof war crimes in the operations.
OL,11,FIn his witness statement, N2252 cited
OL,12,Ffriction over which of the units
OL,13,Fshould carry out certain operational
OL,14,Froles, meaning UKSF3 was "not a
OL,15,Fdisinterested party" in these
OL,16,Finvestigations.
OL,18,FHe said UKSF3 regarded changes to
OL,19,Ftheir responsibilities as a
OL,20,F"relegation" and recalled "a degree of
OL,21,Fsniping at UKSF1 over their conduct".
OL,26,@|D@AOU|D@LO]|D@[OU}D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
