FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780074357
OL,3,CSAS chief avoided police referral to
OL,4,Cprotect troop morale, inquiry hears
OL,6,FN1788 described a breakdown of
OL,7,Frelations with Afghan partner forces.
OL,9,FHe referred to an incident where
OL,10,F"tempers got so frayed" around a
OL,11,Fdiscussion on a deliberate detention
OL,12,Foperation (DDO) that a member of the
OL,13,FAfghan unit pulled a gun on a UKSF
OL,14,Fmentor during a meeting.
OL,16,FSpeaking to ITV News on Friday
OL,17,Fmorning, government minister Torston
OL,18,FBell said that these are "serious
OL,19,Fallegations" but insisted that it was
OL,20,F"important that the inquiry does its
OL,21,Fwork".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
