FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780074357
OL,3,CSAS chief avoided police referral to
OL,4,Cprotect troop morale, inquiry hears
OL,6,FIn contrast, Shadow Defence Minister
OL,7,FDavid Reed insisted "it's important
OL,8,Fthat we back our armed forces" and
OL,9,F"give them the assurance they need"
OL,10,Fand explained that a bigger
OL,11,Fconversation will be needed when the
OL,12,Finquiry concludes.
OL,14,FThe independent inquiry is examining
OL,15,Fwhether the SAS had a policy of
OL,16,Fexecuting males of "fighting age" who
OL,17,Fposed no threat in Afghanistan between
OL,18,F2010 and 2013.
OL,26,@xD@TOUxD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
