OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780074357
OL,3,CSAS chief avoided police referral to
OL,4,Cprotect troop morale, inquiry hears
OL,6,FThe probe is also looking at whether
OL,7,Fthere was an alleged cover-up of
OL,8,Fillegal activity and inadequate
OL,9,Finvestigation by the Royal Military
OL,10,FPolice.
OL,12,FNo charges were brought under
OL,13,FOperation Northmoor, a #10 million
OL,14,Finvestigation set up in 2014 to
OL,15,Fexamine allegations of executions by
OL,16,Fthe SAS, including those of children.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
