OL,3,CSAS chief avoided police referral to
OL,4,Cprotect troop morale, inquiry hears
OL,6,FA further Royal Military Police
OL,7,Finvestigation, codenamed Operation
OL,8,FCestro, resulted in three soldiers
OL,9,Fbeing referred to the Service
OL,10,FProsecuting Authority, but none of
OL,11,Fthem were prosecuted.
OL,13,FThe inquiry continues.
OL,15,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,16,Four political experts are across all
OL,17,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,18,Fto the latest episode below...
